title: #148:  Good Morning, Jonestown With Tony Burkett & Russell Douglas
description:
Thank you for tuning in for another episode of Tin Foil Hat with Sam Tripoli. This episode we welcome from the "Good Morning, Jonestown" podcast, Tony Burkett & Russell Douglas to discuss Jim Jones and what happened that fateful night in Guyana! If you love hearing about the CIA terrorizing everyone and Sam butchering everyone's names than you'll enjoy this instant classic. My new special "Armogeddon" drops this Friday Dec 14th on Vimeo.com.
Rent or Buy here Vimeo.com/OnDemand/Armogeddon
Check out Tony and Russell's podcast at
https://soundcloud.com/goodmorningjonestown
